  <description><![CDATA[<p>Internationally-managed, this charming, small hotel has a cosy atmosphere and offers a friendly welcome. The amazing gardens provide a relaxing setting from which to admire the views of the Jungfrau massif and the quick access to the railway station and bus stop make exploring the region easy. The hotel is located in the heart of Wilderswil, just 2 minutes’ to the railway station and bus stop for the free bus to Interlaken (200m).</p>]]></description>
